................................................................................................13\n3.1 Electricity Demand...................................................................................................................... 13\n3.2 Installed Capacity........................................................................................................................ 13\n3.3 Fuel Prices................................................................................................................................... 15\n3.4 Transmission Network ................................................................................................................ 16\n4. Market Conditions and Background...................................................................................................16\n4.1 ERCOT Market Landscape........................................................................................................... 16\n4.2 Demand and generation ............................................................................................................. 17\n4.3 LP&L Integration ......................................................................................................................... 18\n4.4 HISTORICAL energy prices........................................................................................................... 18\nii\nLIST OF FIGURES\nFigure 1 Generation capacity outage by fuel type. Source: ERCOT..............................................................1\nFigure 2 Annual Average Nodal Price Heat Map...........................................................................................3\nFigure 3 Annual Energy Production by Fuel Type (GWh)..............................................................................4\nFigure 4 Monthly Generation by Fuel Type – 2021 ......................................................................................5\nFigure 5 ERCOT Historical and Projected Wind Generation